# Keep the Docker build context small and reproducible.
# test-runs/ alone can grow to hundreds of GB of soak artefacts and
# must never be tarred into a build context.
#
# NOTE: bin/ is intentionally NOT excluded — the testbed and k8s
# Dockerfiles COPY pre-built binaries (bin/pg_hardstorage and the
# compat shims) straight from it.
.git
.github
test-runs/
site/
dist/
*.exe
*.test
